data.title: Don Miguel
data.text:
Mexican Inspired Flavors

Cooking up delicious Mexican foods since 1908. Each signature recipe features real ingredients, inspired ﬂavors, and a commitment to quality and convenience. Savor your favorites bite by bite at home, or heat and run for quick and easy meals on the go!

Hand held greatness is right around the corner.

Whether you’re looking for a quick snack or a filling meal with just the right ﬂavors, THE BOMB® Burrito is ready to satisfy those really big appetites.

EXPLORE OUR PRODUCTS CLICK HERE

SAVORY INSPIRATION

Perfectly prepared ingredients, inspired creations and all the big, bold Mexican food ﬂavors you love. Crafted in our very own kitchen, each recipe features DON MIGUEL® products for quick, convenient and delicious meals for breakfast, lunch, dinner, and any time in between. View our Inspirations.
